---
const title = "Eqho — Free Offline Dictation. Speak, It Types.";
const description = "Free, open-source dictation for Windows, Linux and macOS. Press a hotkey, speak, and your words appear in any app. 100% offline — your voice never leaves your computer.";
const author = "Daniel Mevit";
const year = 2026;
const releasesUrl = "https://github.com/danielmevit/eqho/releases";
const latestUrl = "https://github.com/danielmevit/eqho/releases/latest";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title}</title>

    <!-- Tab Icons for Light Mode Tabs -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DanielMevit/eqho/main/assets/logo_32_dark.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="64x64" href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DanielMevit/eqho/main/assets/logo_64_dark.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)" />

    <!-- Tab Icons for Dark Mode Tabs -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DanielMevit/eqho/main/assets/logo_32_white.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="64x64" href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DanielMevit/eqho/main/assets/logo_64_white.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)" />

    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="keywords" content="speech to text, voice to text, dictation software, offline speech recognition, free dictation app, voice typing for Windows, OpenAI Whisper app, whisper.cpp GUI, faster-whisper GUI, Vulkan speech to text, AMD GPU dictation, AMD Radeon voice to text, Intel Arc dictation, cross-vendor GPU transcription, runs on any GPU, private speech to text, local voice recognition, no-cloud transcription" />
    <meta name="author" content={author} />

    <!-- Inter Font -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Open Graph for Link Sharing -->
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://danielmevit.github.io/eqho/" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DanielMevit/eqho/main/logo/logo_horizontal_dark.png" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Eqho" />

    <!-- Structured data for search engines + AI scrapers (SoftwareApplication) -->
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
        "name": "Eqho",
        "applicationCategory": "UtilitiesApplication",
        "operatingSystem": "Windows 10 (64-bit), Windows 11 (64-bit), macOS, Linux",
        "description": "Free, offline voice-to-text dictation powered by OpenAI's Whisper. Press a hotkey, speak, and your words appear in any app — 100% local, GPU-accelerated on NVIDIA, AMD, and Intel.",
        "url": "https://danielmevit.github.io/eqho/",
        "downloadUrl": "https://github.com/danielmevit/eqho/releases",
        "softwareVersion": "0.8.6",
        "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Daniel Mevit", "url": "https://github.com/danielmevit" },
        "license": "https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html",
        "isAccessibleForFree": true,
        "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "USD" },
        "keywords": "speech to text, voice typing, offline dictation, OpenAI Whisper, whisper.cpp, faster-whisper, Vulkan speech to text, AMD GPU dictation, cross-vendor GPU transcription, private speech to text, local voice recognition"
      }
    </script>

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0d1117;
        --bg-soft: #10161f;
        --card: #161b22;
        --card-hover: #1b222c;
        --text: #c9d1d9;
        --heading: #ffffff;
        --blue: #58a6ff;
        --blue-deep: #1f6feb;
        --muted: #8b949e;
        --border: #30363d;
        --light-card: #f6f8fa;
        --light-text: #1a1c1f;
        --light-muted: #57606a;
        --radius: 16px;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }

      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }

      img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; }

      .wrap { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

      /* ---------- Nav ---------- */
      nav {
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 1.1rem 0;
      }
      nav .brand img { height: 30px; display: block; }
      nav .links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.4rem; }
      nav a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.95rem; }
      nav a:hover { color: var(--heading); }
      .btn {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.55rem;
        background: var(--blue-deep); color: #fff !important;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.3rem; border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid transparent;
        transition: transform .12s ease, background .12s ease;
      }
      .btn:hover { background: #388bfd; transform: translateY(-1px); }
      .btn.ghost {
        background: transparent; color: var(--text) !important;
        border-color: var(--border);
      }
      .btn.ghost:hover { border-color: var(--muted); }
      .btn.big { padding: 0.95rem 1.7rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }

      /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
      header.hero { padding: 5rem 0 3.5rem; text-align: center; }
      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-block; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue);
        border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; background: var(--bg-soft);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7.5vw, 5rem);
        font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.05;
        color: var(--heading); margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
      }
      h1 .accent { color: var(--blue); }
      .sub {
        font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2.2vw, 1.35rem);
        color: var(--muted); max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 2.2rem;
      }
      .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 0.9rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 0.9rem; }
      .cta-note { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); }

      /* The overlay, recreated: preview panel + the listening pill */
      .overlay-demo { max-width: 640px; margin: 3.2rem auto 0; }
      .overlay-demo .panel {
        background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 18px; padding: 1rem 1.3rem; text-align: left;
        color: var(--text); font-size: 1.02rem; box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
      }
      .overlay-demo .panel .caret {
        display: inline-block; width: 2px; height: 1.05em; background: var(--blue);
        vertical-align: text-bottom; margin-left: 2px; animation: blink 1.1s steps(1) infinite;
      }
      @keyframes blink { 50% { opacity: 0; } }
      .overlay-demo .pill { margin-top: 0.8rem; }
      .overlay-demo .pill img { width: min(380px, 72%); display: block; margin: 0 auto; }

      /* ---------- Sections ---------- */
      section { padding: 4.5rem 0 0; }
      h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--heading);
        margin: 0 0 0.7rem; text-align: center;
      }
      .lede { text-align: center; color: var(--muted); max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 2.6rem; font-size: 1.08rem; }

      .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.1rem; }
      .step {
        background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.6rem;
      }
      .step .num {
        font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue); line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
      }
      .step h3 { color: var(--heading); font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 0 0 0.4rem; }
      .step p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.98rem; }
      .step kbd {
        background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom-width: 2px;
        border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.1rem 0.45rem; font-size: 0.9em; color: var(--heading);
      }

      .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr)); gap: 1.1rem; }
      .card {
        background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.6rem;
        transition: background .12s ease;
      }
      .card:hover { background: var(--card-hover); }
      .card .icon { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }
      .card h3 { color: var(--heading); font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0 0 0.45rem; }
      .card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.97rem; }

      /* ---------- Theme duo (the pill in both worlds) ---------- */
      .duo { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.1rem; }
      .duo .world {
        border-radius: var(--radius); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 2.2rem 1.6rem; text-align: center;
      }
      .duo .world img { width: min(340px, 86%); }
      .duo .world.dark { background: var(--bg-soft); }
      .duo .world.light { background: var(--light-card); border-color: #d0d7de; }
      .duo .world p { margin: 1.1rem 0 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }
      .duo .world.dark p { color: var(--muted); }
      .duo .world.light p { color: var(--light-muted); }

      /* ---------- Screenshot ---------- */
      .shot {
        border-radius: var(--radius); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.5); display: block; margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .langs { text-align: center; color: var(--muted); max-width: 720px; margin: 1.8rem auto 0; line-height: 2; }
      .langs span { white-space: nowrap; }
      .langs span + span::before { content: "·"; color: var(--border); margin: 0 0.55rem; }

      /* ---------- Downloads ---------- */
      .dl-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.1rem; }
      .dl-card {
        background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.7rem;
      }
      .dl-card .os {
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      }
      .dl-card .os svg { width: 30px; height: 30px; fill: var(--heading); flex: none; }
      .dl-card .os h3 { color: var(--heading); margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
      .dl-card .os small { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; }
      .dl-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
      .dl-links a {
        display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
        background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 0.97rem; transition: border-color .12s ease, color .12s ease;
      }
      .dl-links a:hover { border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--heading); }
      .dl-links a .tag { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 400; }
      .dl-links a.primary { background: var(--blue-deep); border-color: transparent; color: #fff; }
      .dl-links a.primary .tag { color: rgba(255,255,255,.75); }
      .dl-links a.primary:hover { background: #388bfd; color: #fff; }
      .dl-fine { text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.88rem; margin-top: 1.6rem; }
      .dl-fine a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }
      .dl-fine a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

      /* ---------- FAQ ---------- */
      .faq { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .faq details {
        background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      }
      .faq summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; color: var(--heading); }
      .faq p { color: var(--muted); margin: 0.8rem 0 0.2rem; }

      /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
      footer {
        margin-top: 5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 2.2rem 0 3rem; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      footer .wrap { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      footer a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
      footer a:hover { color: var(--heading); }
      footer .foot-links { display: flex; gap: 1.3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

      /* ---------- Responsive ---------- */
      @media (max-width: 860px) {
        .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .duo { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        nav .links a.hide-sm { display: none; }
        header.hero { padding-top: 3.2rem; }
        section { padding-top: 3.4rem; }
      }
      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .wrap { padding: 0 1.1rem; }
        .btn.big { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
        .cta-row { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      }
      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        .overlay-demo .panel .caret { animation: none; }
        .btn { transition: none; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="wrap">
      <nav>
        <a class="brand" href="#" aria-label="Eqho home">
          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DanielMevit/eqho/main/logo/logo_horizontal_dark.png" alt="Eqho" height="30" />
        </a>
        <div class="links">
          <a class="hide-sm" href="#how">How it works</a>
          <a class="hide-sm" href="#why">Why Eqho</a>
          <a class="hide-sm" href="changelog">Changelog</a>
          <a class="hide-sm" href="https://github.com/danielmevit/eqho">GitHub</a>
          <a class="btn" href="#downloads">Download</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <header class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <span class="eyebrow">Free · Open source · 100% offline</span>
        <h1>Speak.<br /><span class="accent">It types.</span></h1>
        <p class="sub">
          Eqho turns your voice into text in any app on your computer —
          email, documents, chat, code. No subscription, no account,
          and your voice never leaves your machine.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn big" id="dl-hero" href={latestUrl}>⬇&nbsp; Download for Windows</a>
          <a class="btn big ghost" href="#downloads">All downloads</a>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-note">Also available for Linux and macOS · <span class="rel-version">latest release</span></p>

        <!-- The actual overlay, recreated: your words fill the panel while the pill listens -->
        <div class="overlay-demo" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="panel">This is what dictating with Eqho looks like — your words appear live while you speak<span class="caret"></span></div>
          <div class="pill"><img src="assets/pill_dark.webp" alt="" loading="eager" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="how">
        <div class="wrap">
          <h2>Three steps. That's the whole app.</h2>
          <p class="lede">No setup rituals, no cloud accounts. Install it, pick a voice model once, and dictate.</p>
          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="num">1</div>
              <h3>Click where you want text</h3>
              <p>Any app works — your browser, Word, Slack, a code editor. If you can type there, you can speak there.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="num">2</div>
              <h3>Press <kbd>Alt</kbd> + <kbd>Q</kbd> and talk</h3>
              <p>A small pill appears and listens. Watch your words show up live as you speak. The hotkey is yours to change.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="num">3</div>
              <h3>Press it again — done</h3>
              <p>Your words are typed into the app, cleaned up and capitalized. Say "period" or "new line" if you like dictating punctuation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="why">
        <div class="wrap">
          <h2>Private. Free. Actually yours.</h2>
          <p class="lede">Most dictation tools send your voice to someone's server and charge you monthly for it. Eqho does neither.</p>
          <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">🔒</div>
              <h3>Nothing leaves your computer</h3>
              <p>Speech recognition runs entirely on your machine. No cloud, no account, no audio uploads — ever. The only download is the voice model itself, once.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">💸</div>
              <h3>Free, with no catch</h3>
              <p>No trial, no word limits, no premium tier. Eqho is open source — anyone can read the code and verify every promise on this page.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">⚡</div>
              <h3>Fast on any machine</h3>
              <p>Eqho auto-detects your hardware and uses your graphics card — NVIDIA, AMD, or Intel — for near-instant transcription. No GPU? It runs on CPU too.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="icon">🌍</div>
              <h3>13 languages</h3>
              <p>Tuned for English out of the box, with one-click models for Spanish, German, French, Japanese and more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="wrap">
          <h2>The listening pill</h2>
          <p class="lede">
            When Eqho hears you, you'll know — the pill breathes and ripples with your voice,
            and settles when you pause. It follows your theme, light or dark.
          </p>
          <div class="duo">
            <div class="world dark">
              <img src="assets/pill_dark.webp" alt="Eqho's listening pill in dark theme — flowing blue waves" loading="lazy" />
              <p>Dark theme — deep blues that ride every word.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="world light">
              <img src="assets/pill_light.webp" alt="Eqho's listening pill in light theme — soft blue waves on pearl" loading="lazy" />
              <p>Light theme — frosted glass with the same living wave.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="wrap">
          <h2>Settings you'll actually understand</h2>
          <p class="lede">
            One clean dashboard: pick a voice model by size and accuracy, set your hotkey,
            browse your dictation history, teach it your jargon. That's it.
          </p>
          <img class="shot" src="assets/eqho_app_screenshot.webp" alt="The Eqho dashboard — model picker, hotkey, history and settings" loading="lazy" width="960" />
          <p class="langs">
            <span>English</span><span>Spanish</span><span>Mandarin</span><span>Japanese</span><span>Korean</span><span>Vietnamese</span><span>Arabic</span><span>Ukrainian</span><span>French</span><span>German</span><span>Portuguese</span><span>Russian</span><span>Italian</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="downloads">
        <div class="wrap">
          <h2>Download Eqho</h2>
          <p class="lede">Version <span class="rel-version">latest</span> · free under the AGPL-3.0 open-source license.</p>
          <div class="dl-grid">
            <div class="dl-card">
              <div class="os">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 5.1 10.6 4v7.5H3V5.1zm0 13.8 7.6 1.1v-7.4H3v6.3zM11.4 3.9 21 2.5v9H11.4V3.9zm0 16.2 9.6 1.4v-9H11.4v7.6z"/></svg>
                <h3>Windows <small>Windows 10 / 11, 64-bit</small></h3>
              </div>
              <div class="dl-links">
                <a class="primary" id="dl-win-exe" href={latestUrl}><span>Installer (.exe)</span><span class="tag">recommended</span></a>
                <a id="dl-win-zip" href={latestUrl}><span>Portable (.zip)</span><span class="tag">no install</span></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dl-card">
              <div class="os">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2c-1.9 0-3.2 1.1-3.4 3-.1 1.2 0 2.3-.3 3.3-.4 1.1-1.4 2-2.1 3.2-.9 1.4-1.5 3.2-1 5 .1.3.3.4.4.1.2-.5.6-.9 1.2-1 .1.9.6 1.7 1.2 2.3.4.5.6 1.1 1.2 1.5.8.6 2.1.7 2.8.6.7-.1 1.3-.1 2 0 .7.1 2-.1 2.8-.6.6-.4.8-1 1.2-1.5.6-.6 1.1-1.4 1.2-2.3.6.1 1 .5 1.2 1 .1.3.3.2.4-.1.5-1.8-.1-3.6-1-5-.7-1.2-1.7-2.1-2.1-3.2-.3-1-.2-2.1-.3-3.3C15.2 3.1 13.9 2 12 2zm-1.6 5.6c.4 0 .8.4.8.9s-.4.9-.8.9-.8-.4-.8-.9.4-.9.8-.9zm3.2 0c.4 0 .8.4.8.9s-.4.9-.8.9-.8-.4-.8-.9.4-.9.8-.9zm-1.6 2.6 1.9 1c.3.2.3.5 0 .7l-1.6.9c-.2.1-.4.1-.6 0l-1.6-.9c-.3-.2-.3-.5 0-.7l1.9-1z"/></svg>
                <h3>Linux <small>X11 · 64-bit</small></h3>
              </div>
              <div class="dl-links">
                <a class="primary" id="dl-linux-appimage" href={latestUrl}><span>AppImage</span><span class="tag">run anywhere</span></a>
                <a id="dl-linux-tar" href={latestUrl}><span>Archive (.tar.gz)</span><span class="tag">manual</span></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dl-card">
              <div class="os">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16.6 12.9c0-2 1.6-3 1.7-3.1-1-1.4-2.4-1.6-2.9-1.6-1.2-.1-2.4.7-3 .7-.6 0-1.6-.7-2.6-.7-1.3 0-2.6.8-3.3 2-1.4 2.4-.4 6 1 8 .7 1 1.5 2 2.5 2 1 0 1.4-.6 2.6-.6 1.2 0 1.6.6 2.6.6 1.1 0 1.8-1 2.5-2 .8-1.1 1.1-2.2 1.1-2.3-.1 0-2.2-.8-2.2-3zM14.6 6c.5-.7.9-1.6.8-2.5-.8 0-1.7.5-2.3 1.2-.5.6-.9 1.5-.8 2.4.9.1 1.8-.4 2.3-1.1z"/></svg>
                <h3>macOS <small>Apple Silicon &amp; Intel</small></h3>
              </div>
              <div class="dl-links">
                <a class="primary" id="dl-mac-dmg" href={latestUrl}><span>Disk image (.dmg)</span><span class="tag">drag to install</span></a>
                <a href="https://github.com/danielmevit/eqho#platform-notes"><span>First-launch notes</span><span class="tag">unsigned app</span></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="dl-fine">
            Unsigned builds show a security prompt on first run — that's normal for
            independent open-source apps (<a href="https://github.com/danielmevit/eqho#platform-notes">how to get past it</a>).
            Prefer a package manager? <code>winget install eqho</code> ·
            All versions on the <a href={releasesUrl}>releases page</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="faq">
        <div class="wrap">
          <h2>Fair questions</h2>
          <p class="lede">&nbsp;</p>
          <div class="faq">
            <details>
              <summary>Is my voice really never uploaded?</summary>
              <p>Really. Transcription runs on your own processor or graphics card, using state-of-the-art open speech models (OpenAI's Whisper family). Eqho touches the network exactly once: to download the voice model you pick. The code is open — you can check.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>What's the catch? Why is it free?</summary>
              <p>No catch. Eqho is an open-source project licensed under AGPL-3.0. There is no premium tier, no trial clock, and no word counter.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>How accurate is it?</summary>
              <p>Whisper-class accuracy — the same model family used by professional transcription services. You choose the trade-off: smaller models are faster, bigger ones are more accurate. The default is a sweet spot for everyday English.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>What do I need to run it?</summary>
              <p>A 64-bit computer running Windows 10/11, Linux (X11) or macOS, and about 2&nbsp;GB of disk for the app plus your chosen voice model. A graphics card makes it faster but isn't required.</p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

